headline: Beauty and Cosmetics Retailer Q1 Earnings: Ulta (NASDAQ:ULTA) is the Best in the Biz
summary: Looking back on beauty and cosmetics retailer stocks’ Q1 earnings, we examine this quarter’s best and worst performers, including Ulta (NASDAQ:ULTA) and its peers.
